{
  "texts": [
    "The processing times with the A100 GPU were similar to the processing times from the OpenAI API for the 1, 3, and 5 shot experiments.",
    "For the 10-shot experiments the processing time doubled.",
    "We will now evaluate the performance of our six prompting methods using 10-fold cross-validation for the test set of 1,034 NL/SPARQL-pairs.",
    "This results in inferencing a total of 10,340 queries.",
    "As a baseline experiment, we use the simple prompts introduced in Section 3.1."
  ]
}